Package domain

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Algorithm
    Interface of of the algorithms JPEG, LZ78, LZSS, LZW
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgorithmSet
    AlgorithmSet is a global point to access the different algorithms available, by accessing the algorithms using this reference the instances are initiated only once and thus they become Singleton instances
    AutoAlgorithm
    The AutoAlgorithm is responsible for compressing and decompressing multiple files automatically given a specific algorithm and compression quality (JPEG) It is also responsible for saving stats of all the compressions made of all the files.
    GlobalStats
    These is the class to store the global stats of all the aplication
    Huffman
    This is the essential part of the encoding of the JPEG.
    Huffman.TreeNode
    Class that implements a node of the HuffmanTree
    JPEG
    This is one of the algortihm to compress files, in specific, it compress image files.
    LZ78
    LZ78 ASCII compression algorithm
    LZSS
    LZSS ASCII compression algorithm
    LZW
    LZW ASCII compression algorithm
    PhysicalFile
    PhysicalFile is a representation of a File and the different qualities it has, such as the name, the path, a relative path, the extension.
    Stats
    Class Stats with all the local stats of each compression
    Tree
    The type Tree.
    Utils
    Utils is a global class for all the domain package, this class implements few functions that could be useful for our Algortihms
